feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rbt1665703251337.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rbt1665703251337.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rbt1665703251337.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rbt1665703251337\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">$WEBKEY\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies a unique string to be used as a key in calculating the hash-values used to\n    protect non-editable fields from being modified in a web browser.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"rbt1665703251337__topic_d143756e1_d143757e1_d143758e1\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"rbt1665703251337__note_N1001F_N1001A_N10017_N10001\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> Deprecated (although still\n        accepted). Use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SERVER_SECRET</span> in the [WEB] section instead.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rbt1665703251337__p_d143759e1_d143760e1_d143761e1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$WEBKEY</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> }\n          <var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rbt1665703251337__section_m1j_pxm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d373354e70\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"rbt1665703251337__table_d17372e1_d17373e1_d17374e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><span class=\"ph filepath\">wasv.asn</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Generated during installation</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rbt1665703251337__section_rnp_txm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d373354e117\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"rbt1665703251337__p_d143768e1_d143769e1_d143770e1\">This setting is an alias for\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SERVER_SECRET</span> in the [WEB] section of the assignment file. If both are\n        defined, Uniface will use the last value defined. For more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dqd1713426128184.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dqd1713426128184.html\" title=\"Specifies a unique string to be used as a key in calculating the hash-values used to protect non-editable fields from being modified in a web browser.\">$SERVER_SECRET</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"note caution note_caution\" id=\"rbt1665703251337__note_bq1_5xm_lwb\"><span class=\"note__title\">CAUTION:</span> The key should be kept secret,\n      so you need to control access to the assignment file of the Web Application Server (by\n      default, <span class=\"ph filepath\">wasv.asn</span>) so that only the Uniface Server\n        (<code class=\"ph codeph\">userver</code>) process can read it.</div>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"rbt1665703251337__pre_f41_5xm_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[SETTINGS]\n$WEBKEY = JIOhcvjsqj8vsadv;394hwe028*&amp;^ijhe8762l;v93kns2-0gvr;b-05nm2k3;lkcv;flb0-76-u76-0g45nj348h&amp;^Z</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/key1665702908800.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Web Application Configuration and Deployment</a><p>When you deploy and configure the web application you need to ensure that the application is securely deployed. To do so, the passwords and security mechanisms provided with Uniface must be changed and secured.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531518\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531518\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$WEBKEY Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $WEBKEY Specifies a unique string to be used as a key in calculating the hash-values used to protect non-editable fields from being modified in a web browser. Note: Deprecated (although still accepted). Use $SERVER_SECRET in the [WEB] section instead. $WEBKEY { = } Value Defaults Assignment file: wasv.asn Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: Generated during installation Description This setting is an alias for $SERVER_SECRET in the [WEB] section of the assignment file. If both are defined, Uniface will use the last value defined. For more information, see $SERVER_SECRET . CAUTION: The key should be kept secret, so you need to control access to the assignment file of the Web Application Server (by default, wasv.asn ) so that only the Uniface Server ( userver ) process can read it. [SETTINGS] $WEBKEY = JIOhcvjsqj8vsadv;394hwe028*&^ijhe8762l;v93kns2-0gvr;b-05nm2k3;lkcv;flb0-76-u76-0g45nj348h&^Z Copy Related Links Web Application Configuration and Deployment When you deploy and configure the web application you need to ensure that the application is securely deployed. To do so, the passwords and security mechanisms provided with Uniface must be changed and secured. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}